      121.93,
      543.08,
      135.21
    ],
    "text": "Sergeant Buddhika Karunasinghe, to meet with Squadron Leader Sumedha Ritigala. Further, he",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      142.57,
      543.05,
      155.85
    ],
    "text": "reached Vauniya at or around 10.00 p.m. on that day and met with his friends. At or around 1.00",
