      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      274.84,
      542.97,
      288.12
    ],
    "text": "he was doing in that area at that time. Hence, the petitioner produced his identity card and identified",
